his new motorcycle.

24:22.294 --> 24:23.796
(laughs)
A motorcycle?

24:23.830 --> 24:26.198
No, that's crazy.
Don't worry.

24:26.232 --> 24:28.901
He was with Dr. Hart. I'm sure
she insisted he wear his helmet.

